reviewText: i had expected funny comedians since its a paul rodriguez presentation but i was disapointed. would not recommend it to anybody
this is an excellent buy and to watch it with friends and family is highly recommended

Paul Rodriguez does a great job selecting these rising comedians. My only disapointment is he doesn't appear himself. He only hosts the show. But overall, this dvd was a blast! I loved every minute, especially the final comedian, Jual Villareal. If you're a latino comedy enthusiast, you're guaranteed to love this dvd.
